The,HubSpot,Social,Media,API,allows,developers,to,get,create,and,cancel,broadcast,messages,for,publishing,channels,e,g,a,Twitter,profile,or,a,Facebook,page,The,API,can,also,be,used,to,get,details,on,one,or,more,publishing,channels,HubSpot,provides,a,stack,of,products,that,include,customer,relationship,management,marketing,and,sales,services